#Method bool setRects(const SkIRect rects[], int count)
#In incomplete
#Line # incomplete ##

Set this region to the union of an array of rects. This is generally
faster than calling region.op(rect, kUnion_Op) in a loop. If count is
0, then this region is set to the empty region. #Param rects  incomplete ##
#Param count  incomplete ##

#Return  true if the resulting region is non-empty
##

#Example
// incomplete
##

